e":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:14:55.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n你搞咁多乜鳩健康碼<br />\n到頭來又係只睇身份證簽發地睇到係石家莊簽發就唔俾入<br />\n咁要個健康碼嚟把撚<br />\n定係連中國人都知健康碼其實係鳩做信唔過？"},{"pid":"dac17a4166a893857821074318ec540e9cecd356","tid":2368954,"uid":221211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"造謠生事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ab22d1f123734220e3df7f7c0b762ce1ec9405","tid":2368954,"uid":362366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"李丁只好與陌生的女同學合住酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c100b61e5c8f1a2dabd6704bf70e6ba08c71667","tid":2368954,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c948d75fe28a6337b6cb8b7b3937140588f812e","tid":2368954,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被隔離後，僅是幾塊雞胸肉和一份飯，就花了60元（約72港元），李青在過去9天，在食宿花了2,000元（約2,400港元）。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快D凍死 / 餓死 PLEASE <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"應該一日三餐食康師傅泡麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65572f6727f27eef1ca121f8eb6476f4a6dfd446","tid":2368954,"uid":4964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2cb8fc053034b81474aea7276cc780334d60a879","tid":2368954,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T16:04:30.000Z","msg":"石獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XsbHhiE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXsbHhiE.png&h=0f9997b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/V8GVm2U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.c